{"tid":2429600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又抽中藍屍]香港民研：林鄭民望升 2.9 分　創反送中運動以來新高","createTime":"2021-03-02T12:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:36:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8509c2a9a192aefd8b06f77356dbd1946712f2a4","tid":2429600,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:17:25.000Z","msg":"基本盤無改變，一樣4成0分，佢評分上落高低係視乎抽唔抽中深藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%8D%87-2-9-%E5%88%86-%E5%89%B5%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%258D%2587-2-9-%25E5%2588%2586-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQAz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=7fee0680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A0%2594-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%258D%2587-2-9-%25E5%2588%2586-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&h=a77bff86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E7%A0%94-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E5%8D%87-2-9-%E5%88%86-%E5%89%B5%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E4%BB%A5%E4%BE%86%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港民意研究計劃（香港民研）公布最新特首民望結果。特首林鄭月娥的最新評分為 33.9 分，比 2 月初上升 2.9 分，是 19 年 6 月反修例運動以來的新高，而對特區政府表現的滿意率淨值亦大升 12 個百分點，創下 19 年 5 月以來的高位。<br />\n<br />\n另外，支持林鄭月娥出任特首的比率有 23%，反對率則為 67%，民望淨值為負 43%，雖然仍為負數，但就有所改善，比 2 月初顯著上升 9 個百分點。有 39% 受訪者給予林鄭月娥 0 分。<br />\n</strong><br />\n特區政府表現方面，最新滿意率淨值為負 33 個百分點，顯著上升 12 個百分點，是 2019 年 5 月以來新高；信任淨值為負 14 個百分點，亦是 2019 年 3 月以來新高。<br />\n<br />\n至於市民對現時政治、民生及經濟狀況的滿意淨值則繼續是負數，數字與上個月比較分別不大，其中對政治狀況的滿意淨值為負 42 百分點，是 2018 年 12 月以來新高。<br />\n<br />\n香港民研在 2 月 24 至 26 日，隨機抽樣電話訪問 18 歲或以上香港居民，成功樣本數目為 1,000 人。民研又指，在調查期間，財政司司長陳茂波發表財政預算案，政府將分期發放 5,000 元電子消費券。"},{"pid":"9d76bccb5a63055eb938ab96ef1dc3a7e05f17f0","tid":2429600,"uid":393530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:19:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b2df1b39dcd3aba5bb13ea588d8f7a4148be7fb6","tid":2429600,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"Keyboard man <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c30b072b32eda401f4a1b8ad575618d4fb1f99","tid":2429600,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"有 39% 受訪者給予林鄭月娥 0 分。<br />\n好似keep 住40%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8cd23c989939b58c947ea042f9541e1e2dae53","tid":2429600,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"講真越來越多人唔敢做民調"},{"pid":"6ba01a15d8f49b7423919884a10a2ad7421088fb","tid":2429600,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f8cd23c989939b58c947ea042f9541e1e2dae53","tid":2429600,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"講真越來越多人唔敢做民調"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:37:08.000Z","msg":"的確"},{"pid":"071c42dbbf6962e755b8d7a935f9693a3b055f68","tid":2429600,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T12:38:25.000Z","msg":"特首好波！<br />\n支持特首！<br />\n我愛林鄭！"},{"pid":"c68212b2d6400ee80333c9e821da82dd74a27cc5","tid":2429600,"uid":322110,"like":0,"dislike